cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.IT 

This paper deals with multiview representation learning, which is a popular topic in machine learning and data analysis. The paper proposes a nonconvex formulation for this problem and uses stochastic gradient descent (SGD) methods to solve it efficiently. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and information theory (cs.IT).
